<mjml>
  <mj-head>
	<!-- CSS-STYLE -->
	<mj-style inline="inline"> p, li {margin:0 !important; padding:0; line-height:1.4em;}
	</mj-style>
  </mj-head>
  <!-- BODY -->
  <mj-body background-color="#f4f4f4">
	<mj-section padding-top="40px" background-color="#ffffff">
	  <mj-column>
		<mj-text font-size="11px" align="center">
		  <p>
			<span data-fr-verified="true"><span data-fr-verified="true" class="atwho-inserted">{webview_text}</span>⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠</span>
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-spacer>
		</mj-spacer>
		<mj-image src="{{ getOverridableUrl('images/placeholder-logo.png') }}" width="70px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-top="0px">
		</mj-image>
	  </mj-column>
	</mj-section>
	<mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding-top="0px">
	  <mj-column>
		<mj-text font-size="24px" align="center" font-weight="700">
		  <p>Start customizing your email
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-spacer align="center">
		</mj-spacer>
		<mj-image src="{{ getOverridableUrl('images/placeholder-image.png') }}" padding-right="0px" padding-left="0px" padding-bottom="0px">
		</mj-image>
	  </mj-column>
	</mj-section>
	<mj-section background-color="#ffffff">
	  <mj-column width="530px">
		<mj-text font-size="16px" align="center">
		  <p>Design a standout email by strategically placing content blocks in key areas. Test different layouts to maximize reader engagement and conversion.
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-spacer height="40px">
		</mj-spacer>
		<mj-text font-size="22px" font-weight="700" align="center">
		  <p>For e-commerce businesses
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-text font-size="16px" align="center">
		  <p>Engage customers at every stage: welcome new buyers, reconnect with inactive shoppers, or reward loyal patrons with exclusive offers.
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-spacer align="center">
		</mj-spacer>
		<mj-text font-size="22px" font-weight="700" align="center">
		  <p>For service-based businesses
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-text font-size="16px" align="center">
		  <p>Nurture your email list: greet new subscribers warmly, express gratitude to event attendees, and reach out to dormant contacts with a friendly reminder.
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-spacer>
		</mj-spacer>
		<mj-button href="https://" background-color="#000000" inner-padding="16px 32px" border-radius="0px 0px 0px 0px" font-size="16px">
		  <p>Call to action here
		  </p>
		</mj-button>
		<mj-spacer align="center">
		</mj-spacer>
		<mj-divider border-width="2px" border-color="#d0d0d0">
		</mj-divider>
		<mj-spacer height="40px">
		</mj-spacer>
		<mj-text font-size="22px" font-weight="700" align="center">
		  <p>Highlight recent events
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-text font-size="16px" align="center">
		  <p>Inform your readers about your latest activities and important updates they may have overlooked.
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-spacer>
		</mj-spacer>
	  </mj-column>
	</mj-section>
	<mj-section padding-top="0" padding-bottom="20px" background-color="#000000">
	  <mj-column>
		<mj-spacer height="40px">
		</mj-spacer>
		<mj-image src="{{ getOverridableUrl('images/placeholder-logo-inverse.png') }}" width="70px" padding-bottom="0px">
		</mj-image>
		<mj-spacer>
		</mj-spacer>
		<mj-text font-family="Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" line-height="1.5" align="center" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" font-size="12px" color="white">
		  <p>Amazing Company
			<br/>11111 Beautiful City, 1212 Nice Street
			<br/>Brazil
			<br/>
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-spacer>
		</mj-spacer>
		<mj-text font-size="11px" align="center" color="#a1a1a1">
		  <p>Fancy seeing you down here. You’re getting this email because you gave us your email address.
		  </p>
		  <p>Want to change how you receive these emails?
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-text font-size="11px" align="center" color="#a1a1a1">
		  <p>
			<span data-fr-verified="true"><span data-fr-verified="true" class="atwho-inserted">{unsubscribe_text}</span>⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠</span>
		  </p>
		</mj-text>
		<mj-spacer>
		</mj-spacer>
	  </mj-column>
	</mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
